(645, 'canifs', 'Wrangler', 'Wrangler yellowhorse', 'The custom handle is inlayed with desert ironwood, blue turquoise, rare white turquoise and jaspe. The nickel silver bolsters are hand sculpted. Nickel silver buffalo inlay. Serialized limited edition of 100 knives --> nr 48/100', 'wryllowh-380.jpg', 'voir description', '420hc', 'fermé : 12 cm', NULL, 470, NULL, 0, NULL, 1),
